#. js-lingui-id: yHUdh6
#: src/case-studies/case-study-stories.ts
msgid "AC&T Education Migration (actimmi.com) is an education agency in Australia. They help international students with applications to education providers and visas. They had been on a previous CRM until the vendor shut the system down, leaving nothing but a CSV export."
